---
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import { CrewStats } from '../components/CrewStats';
import DiscordInvite from '../components/DiscordInvite.astro';
import YouTube from '../components/YouTube.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to GPAD">
	<p>We are an active and supportive GTA Online crew, and game community.</p>

	<p>
		Our community supports <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-200 font-black"
			>Playstation 5</span
		> and <span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-200 font-black">Xbox Series X|S</span> players.
	</p><p>
		In addition to being a GTA crew, our members also play other multiplayer games together such as
		Minecraft, Call of Duty and Forza.
	</p>

	<!-- <YouTube videoId="ulKZbFzPZyw" title="Welcome to GPAD" class="my-4" /> -->
	<img src="/post-op.webp" loading="lazy" alt="How we do things at GPAD" class="my-4" />

	<Card class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
		<CrewStats client:only="preact" />
	</Card>

	<p>
		We have an active discord community where members can game together, and share experiences
		outside of gaming.
	</p>

	<h2 title="Did I stutter? Yes, Payd.">Come to our house and get payd!</h2>

	<p>
		Join our{' '}
